Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:41.92,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\blur9\pos(1851,546)}从心底溢了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:47.21,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\blur9\pos(1851,546)}想象被世界渐渐敲响
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:51.71,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\blur9\pos(1851,546)}呐呐、告诉我古怪未来的你
