Comment: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,————————Text-PartA————————
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:38.88,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:41.14,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙要让人等到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:44.38,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,到底干什么才能那么花时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:46.74,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.11,0:01:49.59,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,从那家伙出去已经过去多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:50.86,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,三天！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.06,0:01:52.69,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,已经无话可说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:54.82,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙到底有多蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:59.60,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,再说那家伙应该也是被村民排斥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.02,0:02:03.54,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,慢吞吞如果再出了什么事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:04.55,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,别生气别生气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:09.17,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈要穿的…婚纱来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:13.02,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是找那个花了很多时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.88,0:02:15.25,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.58,0:02:17.34,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这样也没办法了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:20.93,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就算是这样也太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:25.48,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,他的寿命也没有长到可以这样挥霍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:33.32,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  爸爸不是说会一起来  永远在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:35.96,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈不幸福吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:39.20,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,当然幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:41.78,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,那就再稍微等一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:49.98,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  时间静止的世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:53.03,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里会是什么感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:54.86,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样？妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:57.50,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:09.23,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,这种地方竟然有房子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:13.24,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的距离为什么到现在都没人发现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:16.22,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(930,990)}TSUKIHIKO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:16.22,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是掳走少年兵的怪物的腹地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:22.47,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,但是少年兵那家伙说怪物是自己的妻子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:25.31,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物是少年兵的妻子？怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:29.91,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是怪物用妖术操纵了少年兵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:34.52,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,想要通过操纵少年兵  有朝一日袭击村子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:36.98,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,如果变成那样只能够处理掉少年兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:40.26,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你们听好  趁早干完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:43.81,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:46.57,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,你磨蹭个什么  走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:52.26,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:55.10,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么…刚才好像有脚步声…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:56.95,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸回来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:03:59.31,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,少年兵吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:03.75,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(813,990)}SHION
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:03.75,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑  别过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:08.69,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉了吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:11.39,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  果断一发解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:13.85,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.78,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  这是怪物的女儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:18.63,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}妈妈…！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:19.54,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,那头发  肯定没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:21.66,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  把这家伙也干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:25.31,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…喂  她还很小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:26.92,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.80,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,磨磨蹭蹭的搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:30.91,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  让我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.59,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目隐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:35.20,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？！消失了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:37.53,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…妖术？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:38.68,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:44.62,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:46.19,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:49.42,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目欺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:55.14,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目夺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:00.43,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:11.56,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,东躲西藏也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.73,0:05:13.76,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,纵使逃至天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:16.18,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,尔等所在之处也立可知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.41,0:05:18.77,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,少年兵怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:19.82,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,快说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:25.36,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不愿直言则读透汝心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:27.55,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目窃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:33.80,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  快说怪物在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:38.36,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不然…我们也不想打你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:42.15,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…也不能放任来历不明的东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:46.58,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(741,990)}AZAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:46.58,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,薊…薊是我的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:49.05,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不准…出手！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:52.54,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  为什么要包庇那个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:54.20,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,你是人类吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:58.02,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,还要反抗的话…不会轻饶你！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:00.09,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不是包庇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:02.60,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不是全部说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:07.95,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和她…和家人永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:09.42,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:10.02,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:14.69,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！似乎发现信号一类的东西了  一直延续到森林那边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:15.99,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:20.55,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,是少年兵为回去而准备的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:22.92,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,立即为退治怪物做准备！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:26.40,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多给我清醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:29.33,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,把她解决掉后  你也会清醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:31.18,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  快点做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:32.67,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:37.58,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:38.87,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,滚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:41.03,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:44.10,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,然后永远不许带任何人来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.68,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了就赶快给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:53.12,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,少年兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:08.89,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:11.48,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑  别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:14.58,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,别再靠近我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:18.45,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再因我而让你们受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:20.59,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:22.27,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是太笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.65,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,想要逃避世间之理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:27.82,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,并且还把你们也牵连进来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:31.76,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,其实已经意识到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.75,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有我在就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:41.50,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,只要没有我  你们就能在这个世界上幸福地生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:44.87,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我没有祈盼幸福…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:48.79,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,只是稍微做了一会梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:52.51,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,能永远和家人生活在一起的幻想…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:55.17,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,太美好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:57.68,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,你们真是无可救药得美好…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.69,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈！不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:04.21,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑  你不是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:06.61,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要使用这种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:09.86,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我没有这样说的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:14.91,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,但你要作为一个人类  和父亲一起幸福地生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:18.30,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我的…幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:20.99,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！妈妈别走！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:26.35,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  对不起  对不起  对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:28.55,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,永远爱你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:34.54,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,我会永远祈祷你们能幸福  永远…
Comment: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,————————Text-PartB————————
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉这样不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又想要擅自出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  别说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你读连环画
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是哦  可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到这里一起读吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那今天就读这个故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那天开始  从妈妈留下我们消失那天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底过了多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸去世的时候  茉莉呱呱坠地的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈都没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈现在也在那个没有终结的世界一个人生活着么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我一人等待着不知会不会归来的妈妈也好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等茉莉再大些  就让她见见外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界肯定会接受她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像妈妈对我所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在对我来说茉莉的幸福就是我的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  不知道什么时候睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.69,0:10:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.97,0:11:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉！在就应答我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？喂  怪物不是说只有一只吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.53,0:11:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别老想着以前的传说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也靠它找到了有意思的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊  这头发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候做成展示品的话肯定能大赚一笔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼  住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个  放开那孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？区区个怪物说点什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实点！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:12:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  要把他也一起抓了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你在听我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  妈妈  我们…没有变得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到  连她们也拉进这边了  您真是坏心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个永不结束的世界的痛苦您不是最清楚的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:12:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  不会闭嘴的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺从于利己又轻松的欲望  创造出这个世界的不正是大人您吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来您的愿望是把最爱的家人一起带到这里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是很好嘛  女儿和孙女一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿望终于实现了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.27,0:13:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起  真是愚蠢  没错  没错  就要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是我们的最大的快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑  这都是我的错  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  就是这个表情  太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  对  就是这样  变成这种悲剧全都是因为您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少  至少只有这孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己丢掉了女王蛇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被那个附身的话  确实能救那孩子一命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  这样也就没有抑制这个世界的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附身于您的蛇失去了女王是多么的混乱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请放心吧  至少不会寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您对这世界所下达的把8月15日逝去的生命卷进来这条命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是无法停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办  要是不离家出走就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且都是修哉不好  都是修哉欺负人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不听使唤地…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  你和家人走散了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许我也和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红色的眼睛也是一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  不要再走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁…来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是…女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都是一个人  好寂寞  一个人好寂寞啊  谁来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来  不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到我眼睛的话就会变成石头的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石头？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…我必须得是一个人  所以请回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼唤我的人就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  我和你是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都被别人忌讳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全用不着害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…那个…做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.68,0:18:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  我睡着了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  他去哪里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都太过分了  把我丢下一起走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  有人在睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吗  会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口…口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  请喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不烫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  嗯  不烫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.61,0:19:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害  你是从哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会在那里睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢  不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  记性不怎么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记性不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也经常忘记东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然觉得要是能都记得就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思议呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.27,0:19:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一个  我还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么  是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要朋友  想和朋友一起玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋…友？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  但是我只记得这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和朋友一起玩耍  只有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.89,0:20:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就和我做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以介绍我的朋友给你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…大家一定很乐意…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已经深夜0时了  还有如此人群
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信  到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如您所见  非常的吵闹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:20:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  能听到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:20:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上是从现场发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也去吧  大家一定都在那里的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.80,0:21:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的朋友
Comment: 0,0:22:40.93,0:22:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,————————Text-PartC————————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.48,0:22:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女失去了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.71,0:22:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的重要的朋友  全都不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:22:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女一个人哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.01,0:23:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想再一次和大家一起玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.10,0:23:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女无数次如此祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.08,0:23:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么向少女搭话了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实现您的愿望吧  实现您的渴望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为您带来一个能实现您的空想的世界吧
